Package: rasterSp
Type: Package
Title: R Package to rasterize and summarise IUCN range maps
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2023-01-02
Authors@R: 
    person("RS-eco", email = "RS-eco@posteo.de", role = c("cre", "aut"))
Maintainer: RS-eco <RS-eco@posteo.de>
Description: R Package for accessing and processing IUCN range map data. Most importantly, it contains functions for rasterizing species distribution shapefiles (as obtained from IUCN or BirdLife) or point data (as obtained from eBird or GBIF).
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: readr, dplyr, raster, methods, data.table, tidyselect
Suggests: ggplot2, sf, rgdal, sp, knitr, terra, fasterize, rmarkdown, parallel
License: GPL (>= 3)
LazyData: TRUE
LazyDataCompression: xz
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: no
Author: RS-eco [cre, aut]
URL: https://github.com/RS-eco/rasterSp
BugReports: https://github.com/RS-eco/rasterSp/issues
